Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.67,0:00:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.62,0:00:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a big ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.44,0:00:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called the Ostland.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.94,0:00:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the latest exploration ship made based on Mr. Jean Colbert's design.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Zerbst invested in my research.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.35,0:00:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it's the fruit of our love!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.31,0:00:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, we've been away on a test flight these past few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.90,0:00:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But last night, the wind pushed us off course\Nand we happened to be flying around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.30,0:00:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we saw you fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.15,0:00:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really surprised us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.78,0:00:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It surprised me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.31,0:01:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I saw you and heard your familiar voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.63,0:01:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.11,0:01:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.69,0:01:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I honestly thought you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.81,0:01:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It turns out Tabitha cast a spell to stop one's\Nheart temporarily to make one appear dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.21,0:01:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took him out of the coffin as soon as she told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I had him stay at my house in Germania.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.86,0:01:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you keep it a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.98,0:01:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why couldn't you have told us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.59,0:01:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.18,0:01:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I meant to, but I never found the right time to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.63,0:01:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for making you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I'm glad to know that you are well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.07,0:01:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Colbert-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you don't need to tell the others you fought that Gallian girl the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I should, but... I can't make sense of it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Tabitha do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has that look again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:03:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been like that since this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I forgive him so easily, my dignity as his master will fade!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.65,0:04:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.74,0:04:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.63,0:04:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.87,0:04:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The incident with the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Oh, that"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we already talked about it last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Just how things turned out", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.07,0:04:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think about it, that's not an explanation at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a clearer story.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I've been a little forgetful these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think the master is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me exactly what happened that led to that situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.88,0:04:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gathering the Order of Undine Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:04:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll talk about it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell the whole story, she says...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I really can't, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Vallière.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.65,0:05:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't heard the result yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What result?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether Saito-san found you at the ball last night or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from your reaction, he didn't, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.67,0:05:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-There was an emergency yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making excuses is what sore losers do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Praise the Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long live Her Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Henrietta-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is a magnificent ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be spoken of in all Halcheginia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an honour, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you used this ship to repel the gargoyles that appeared near the academy last night, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have my gratitude from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than me, you should thank Saito-kun here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito Chevalier de Hiraga-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I give you my gratitude, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.31,0:06:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I am your knight, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.98,0:06:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.65,0:06:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is there a strange atmosphere between them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.89,0:06:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Miss Vallière?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That dog... That dog... That dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.51,0:06:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking? It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dog and the Queen? How ridiculous. Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san and the Queen were h-hugging?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.88,0:06:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! Not so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.99,0:07:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the Queen as a rival, there won't be any chance of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.66,0:07:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk like you had a chance before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I mean, it's the Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She can do whatever she wants!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet she'll eventually make Saito-san work at the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when night falls...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.17,0:07:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "when night falls"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gone that far, so out with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me put it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In chapter two of The Glorious Day of Countess Butterfly, there's a scene that goes like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.44,0:07:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A noble lady invites a knight to her bedroom and says,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"My knight. Serve me the way you wish."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Give me a delusional, sensational joy."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! The Princess would never say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"That's right! Now... come..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.52,0:07:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Right to my breasts!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yes! There! Right there!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:56.12,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:08:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That was this stupid maid putting on an act!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.98,0:08:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colbert-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-kun. Do you know the origin of the name of the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.53,0:08:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ostland.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the East.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I named it hoping to go to the far eastern area with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.89,0:08:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I was able to make this ship is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many things I want to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.09,0:08:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.88,0:08:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The return carriage is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must return to my duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.88,0:09:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a problem, Your Highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.71,0:09:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish to remain here for a little while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.59,0:09:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Such a thing happened between Saito-san and the Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.78,0:09:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem to be too surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.08,0:09:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am, but I think there must be some reason for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course I think so, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.94,0:09:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But because Saito won't say it clearly...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can use this if you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.87,0:09:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a magic item called Last Night Orb.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.27,0:09:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last Night Orb?! I've heard about them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.13,0:10:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you know about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're really popular among the wives in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.42,0:10:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're disposable, so the stock keeps running out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.99,0:10:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you get hold of one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beatrice-san gave it to me to settle things between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can we do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.57,0:10:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you look at a person through this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can see what that person did the previous night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.34,0:10:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear wives use them to check if their\Nhusbands are cheating on them or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that so? But I don't need to use something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe Saito-san, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.30,0:10:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if this makes you feel better...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.51,0:10:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I use this, will this sense of anxiety go away?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.75,0:10:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need it, right, Miss Vallière?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'll use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my familiar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those propellers provide three times the\Npropulsion and allow long-range flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.39,0:11:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it based on your Dragon's Plumage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It runs on coal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The steam pressure from boiling water\Nheated with the coal moves the propellers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to call it the water vapour engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Saito-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.54,0:11:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll see Mr. Colbert's last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.52,0:11:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! It's pretty hard to aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could that be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.84,0:11:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:11:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:11:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.52,0:12:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why do I have to run?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What she had in her hand is a scary item that strips a man of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strips? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep running!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.78,0:12:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The usual, I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.52,0:12:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away, you mutt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.94,0:12:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito! Stop your futile resistance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll split up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:12:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:12:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, what about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the water vapour engine?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.07,0:13:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing how he made this just from looking at the Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.45,0:13:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It brings back memories. There were a lot of these in my world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tiffa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for Louise-san's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you can't, Tiffa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.32,0:13:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surrender, Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:51.76,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:13:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:14:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is where you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.83,0:14:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Miss Zerbst.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.32,0:14:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was tuning things for the next flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.47,0:14:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.99,0:14:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me Kirche.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.10,0:14:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter when there's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop it, Miss{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dear Jean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.36,0:14:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-S{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.07,0:14:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Saito-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you see! T-This is{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry for the disturbance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.38,0:15:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for all the trouble, Dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't run away anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.71,0:15:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last Night Orb.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.69,0:15:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me what Saito did last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.17,0:15:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does it show Tabitha?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was Tabitha involved last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito! Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.10,0:15:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. Tabitha got in my way when I tried to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.74,0:15:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it wasn't of her own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheffield ordered her to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She called Tabitha a faithful watchdog or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting more confusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does Tabitha listen to that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be related to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha isn't an ordinary aristocrat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.93,0:16:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a member of Gallia's royal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her father was the younger brother of the current King.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.72,0:17:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her father was killed during the fight over the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha was also targeted and had her food poisoned,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but her mother took the poison meant for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.74,0:17:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since, her mother's been mentally ill,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,hiding within one room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that the Kingdom of Gallia named Tabitha a\Nchevalier and gave her seemingly impossible missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.29,0:17:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible missions?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.18,0:17:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monster slaying, dangerous scouting and the like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We fought you guys at the Lagdorian Lake, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.79,0:17:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was one of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So yesterday was as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.77,0:17:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it was an order from the Kingdom of Gallia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forgive them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.07,0:17:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Louise. Let's go to Gallia right now and{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. I'm safe here, so Tabitha failed in her mission, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.52,0:17:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's always the chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.77,0:18:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you take her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.08,0:18:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you take Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.08,0:18:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the woman the Gallian Military arrested this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where they took her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Vitartial of Neftes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.85,0:18:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.22,0:18:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.38,0:18:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We elves do not relish needless fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.93,0:19:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I ask you to comply and come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.79,0:19:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the King of Gallia, Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to take you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nature magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not like that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call it the power of spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.89,0:20:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who tried to take Louise away were from Gallia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.41,0:20:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way Tabitha would attack me otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.74,0:20:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.08,0:20:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheffield said she wants my abilities as a void mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness, please let me go to Gallia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.03,0:20:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.58,0:20:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forgive them for trying to kidnap Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.62,0:20:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to use Tabitha for that... It's too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.90,0:20:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll march in and make sure they can't do that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.21,0:20:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.66,0:20:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.10,0:20:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll knock them all out and{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't do such a dangerous thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.04,0:20:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.19,0:20:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We first need to gather evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it is Gallia's doing, then I will use this Kingdom's forces...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to protect you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.01,0:21:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me you won't do anything rash.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.71,0:21:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.93,0:21:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dang. We never figured out what happened last night, did we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.40,0:21:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I couldn't be of any help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.77,0:21:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.39,0:21:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.68,0:21:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that I believe him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:21:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sigh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.58,0:22:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.46,0:22:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.94,0:23:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet another girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.37,0:23:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One after another! You pervert dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.22,0:23:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Searching for her sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.89,0:23:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.19,0:23:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero no Tsukaima. Princess no Rondo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha's Younger Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.12,0:23:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty tough for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you if you look away.
